comments: Harris (PHI) does not release his shot attempt prior to the 24 second shot clock expiring.
Young (ATL) draws Thybulle (PHI) into the air towards him and the contact results in a foul on Thybulle (PHI) even if contact is initiated by Young (ATL).
Harris (PHI) releases the pass and marginal contact occurs with Gallinari (ATL), who is not dislodged from his defensive position as a result of the contact.
Simmons (PHI) is deemed to be imminently exiting the lane within three seconds.
Collins (ATL) cleanly blocks Harris (PHI) during his shot attempt near the basket.
Harris (PHI) makes marginal contact with Collins' (ATL) arm and does not affect his ability to get to the loose ball during the rebound.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ball is deflected out of bounds by Harris (PHI) and ATL is given possession of the ball.
Curry (PHI) legally contests Gallinari's (ATL) jump shot attempt.
Simmons (PHI) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Williams (ATL) and absorbs the incoming contact during the pick.
Embiid (PHI) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Collins (ATL), collapses his arm, and absorbs the incoming contact during the screen.
Gallinari (ATL) moves laterally into Embiid's (PHI) path and makes contact to his body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Young (ATL) makes incidental contact with Thybulle's (PHI) foot as both players attempt to get to the inbounds pass in the backcourt.
Harris (PHI) commits a take foul on Young (ATL).
